---
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const posts = await getCollection("blog");
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>About XXXTentacion</title>

   
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/global.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <Nav />

    <main class="about-wrapper">

      <section class="about-hero">
        <h1 class="about-title">About XXXTentacion</h1>
        <p class="about-subtitle">Jahseh Dwayne Ricardo Onfroy</p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-content">
        <div class="about-image-box">
          <img src="/images/artist.jpg" alt="XXXTentacion" class="about-image">
        </div>

        <div class="about-text">
          <p>
            XXXTentacion was an American rapper, singer, and songwriter known for his raw emotion, vulnerability, and genre-breaking sound.
            His music blended hip-hop, R&B, lo-fi, emo, and alternative influences, creating a style that connected deeply with millions
            of listeners around the world.
          </p>

          <p>
            Emerging from SoundCloud with an experimental and unfiltered approach, he quickly became a cultural phenomenon. His songs often
            explored themes of pain, mental health, personal growth, and emotional struggle, resonating deeply with a generation seeking honesty.
          </p>

          <p>
            Despite a controversial life, his impact on music continues to grow. Projects like <em>17</em> and <em>?</em> remain iconic,
            and his influence can be seen in the rise of emotional rap and alternative trap music.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
